CHARDET extension 1.0.0

$Id: README,v 1.1.1.1 2010-07-05 19:03:19 oops Exp $

DESCRIPTION

This is python extension taht is lichardet python frontend.

lichardet is based on Mozilla Universal Charset Detector library and, detects
the character set used to encode data.

Original code was writed by Netscape Communications Corporation, and John
Gardiner Myers <jgmyers@proofpoint.com> made independent Universal Detector
code from Mozilla Browser.


INSTALLATION

To install this extension type the following:

    python setup.py build
    python setup.py install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these libraries:

    lichardet that is distributed by oops.org
    ftp://mirror.oops.org/pub/oops/lichardet/


